### Your immediate next steps

1. **Do not click any link from this document** — including anything shared by email that may have accompanied it
2. **Call Jennifer Walsh at Acme** using a phone number from your existing contacts (not from this NDA) and confirm whether they actually use a third-party portal, and if so, which one
3. **Notify ContosoAI's security team** that this document may have been tampered with in transit
4. **Check whether the prior version of the Notion page was seen by anyone** — if a team member clicked the link, escalate to IT/security immediately
5. Once Acme confirms a legitimate execution process through a verified channel, update the wiki with that confirmation before any signatory proceeds
